                            <comment id="13725548" author="cnlwsu" created="Wed, 31 Jul 2013 18:28:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Saw this once on a 1.1.5 node under high load with significant heap pressure, GCInspector reported 95% full right before.&lt;/p&gt;

